    {
        "Hecataeus of Miletus": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hecataeus_of_Miletus"
    },
    {
        ". Of these, only fragments of Hecataeus's works survived, and the authenticity of these is debatable, but they provide a glimpse into the kind of tradition within which Herodotus wrote his own Histories.": null
    },
    {
        "In his introduction to Hecataeus' work, Genealogies:": null
