    {
        " refers to a version of The Histories written by \"Herodotus of Thurium\", and some passages in the Histories have been interpreted as proof that he wrote about southern Italy from personal experience there (IV, 15,99; VI, 127). Intimate knowledge of some events in the first years of the ": null
